Package mosaic.palettegenerator

Interface Summary
ColorPaletteGenerator ColorPaletteGenerators return a list of colors.
 

Class Summary
DistributedColorPaletteGenerator Return n colors evenly distributed across the RGB spectrum.
ImageBasedColorPaletteGenerator Generate a color palette of n colors based on the colors found in the image.
ManualColorPaletteGenerator Return the first n colors from a manually-defined list.
RandomColorPaletteGenerator Generate n random colors.
